B.R3=new A.a1("ATC informed the crew that the runway was temporarily closed.","ATC ekibe pistin ge\xe7ici olarak kapat\u0131ld\u0131\u011f\u0131n\u0131 bildirdi.","was temporarily closed")
B.Qx=new A.a1("The maintenance engineer said he would complete the inspection by 0600.","Bak\u0131m m\xfchendisi incelemeyi 06:00'ya kadar tamamlayaca\u011f\u0131n\u0131 s\xf6yledi.","would complete")
