B.XE=new A.m(B.u,"\u26a0\ufe0f \u0130z T\xfcrb\xfclanss\u0131 Kategorileri","**J \u2014 Super** (A380, AN-124): wingspan >80m\n**H \u2014 Heavy** (B747, B777, A330): MTOW >136,000kg\n**M \u2014 Medium** (B737, A320): MTOW 7,000\u2013136,000kg\n**L \u2014 Light** (Cessna, DA-42): MTOW <7,000kg\n\nSeparation minima increase behind heavier aircraft:\n\u2022 H behind J: 6nm\n\u2022 M behind H: 5nm\n\u2022 L behind H: 6nm\n\nWake turbulence is most severe at **low speed, high angle of attack** (on approach)",null,null,null)
B.OL=new A.a1("B738/M in the flight plan means Boeing 737-800 with Medium wake turbulence category.","U\xe7u\u015f plan\u0131ndaki B738/M, Boeing 737-800 ve Orta a\u011f\u0131rl\u0131k kategorisi anlam\u0131na gelir.","/M")
B.QH=new A.a1("EET/LTAA0123 means the estimated elapsed time to the LTAA FIR boundary is 1 hour 23 minutes.","EET/LTAA0123, LTAA FIR s\u0131n\u0131r\u0131na tahmini ge\xe7i\u015f s\xfcresinin 1 saat 23 dakika oldu\u011fu anlam\u0131na gelir.","EET")
