B.Wx=new A.m(B.x,"Edilgenin ileri formlar\u0131","Temel edilgen yap\u0131y\u0131 biliyorsun. \u015eimdi havac\u0131l\u0131k belgelerinde s\u0131k\xe7a kar\u015f\u0131la\u015f\u0131lan **perfect passive**, **causative** (have/get something done) ve **reporting structures** (It is reported that\u2026) \xfczerine yo\u011funla\u015faca\u011f\u0131z.",null,null,null)
