B.a0_=new A.m(B.u,"Temel Yorgunluk Terminolojisi","**FTL** \u2014 Flight Time Limitations (U\xe7u\u015f S\xfcresi S\u0131n\u0131rlamalar\u0131)\n**FRMS** \u2014 Fatigue Risk Management System\n**FDP** \u2014 Flight Duty Period (u\xe7u\u015f g\xf6rev s\xfcresi, raporlamadan kalk\u0131\u015fa)\n**FT** \u2014 Flight Time (blok s\xfcresi)\n**Cumulative fatigue** \u2014 biriken yorgunluk (seferler aras\u0131 tam dinlenme olmaks\u0131z\u0131n)\n**Sleep inertia** \u2014 uyan\u0131\u015f\u0131n hemen ard\u0131ndan gelen bozulmu\u015f performans\n**Circadian rhythm** \u2014 biyolojik saat\n**WOCL** \u2014 Window of Circadian Low (02:00-06:00 aras\u0131; performans en d\xfc\u015f\xfck)\n**Split duty** \u2014 uzun mola i\xe7eren, 2 par\xe7al\u0131 g\xf6rev periyodu\n**Controlled rest** \u2014 kokpitte k\u0131sa uyku (uzun menzilli u\xe7u\u015flarda izinli)",null,null,null)
