B.a0D=new A.m(B.x,"G\xfcmr\xfck formlar\u0131","Uluslararas\u0131 u\xe7u\u015flarda yolculara arrival card (giri\u015f kart\u0131) veya customs declaration form (g\xfcmr\xfck beyan formu) doldurmalar\u0131 i\xe7in kabin ekibi rehberlik eder. Bu belgelerdeki terminoloji standartla\u015ft\u0131r\u0131lm\u0131\u015ft\u0131r.",null,null,null)
B.a_4=new A.m(B.u,"Form Terminolojisi","**Arrival card:**\n\u2022 Surname / Family name \u2014 soyad\u0131\n\u2022 Given names / First name \u2014 ad\u0131\n\u2022 Date of birth (DD/MM/YYYY) \u2014 do\u011fum tarihi\n\u2022 Nationality \u2014 uyruk\n\u2022 Passport number \u2014 pasaport numaras\u0131\n\u2022 Purpose of visit: tourism / business / transit / study\n\u2022 Address in country of destination \u2014 gidilen \xfclkedeki adres\n\n**Customs declaration:**\n\u2022 Do you have goods to declare? \u2014 Beyan edecek e\u015fyanz var m\u0131?\n\u2022 Are you carrying currency exceeding [limit]? \u2014 Limitin \xfczerinde d\xf6viz ta\u015f\u0131yor musunuz?\n\u2022 Are you carrying meat, dairy, or plant products? \u2014 Et, s\xfct veya bitki \xfcr\xfcnleri ta\u015f\u0131yor musunuz?",null,null,null)
